Modified Monash Model polygons (SA1, 2016 edition, polygons with MMM, 2019 edition column)

get_mmm19_poly.Rd

Modified Monash Model polygons (SA1, 2016 edition, polygons with MMM, 2019 edition column)

Usage

get_mmm19_poly(export_dir = tempdir())

Arguments

export_dir

The directory to store the downloaded data.

Value

An sf object.

get_mmm19_poly()
